FBIS3-42180 "jptot005__l94034" JPRS-TOT-94-005-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 2 February 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY Bomb at Diyarbakir Governor's Office Kills 1, Injures 7 TA2501112394 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1100 GMT 25 Jan 94 TA2501112394 Ankara TRT Television Network Language: Turkish Article Type:BFN [Announcer-read report over video] [Text] A bomb exploded on the ground floor of the Diyarbakir Governor's Office building killing one person and wounding seven. Our correspondent has learned that the explosion occurred in the restroom of the Registry at 1000. The bomb was placed by terrorists. One child was killed instantly. The seven injured were taken to hospitals in Diyarbakir. The explosion damaged the building, as well as surrounding buildings.
